      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 20:49:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴里·纳普表示，债券收益率将走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-06/bond-yields-are-headed-higher-barry-knapp-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ironsides 宏观经济研究主管 Barry Knapp 表示，2025 年上半年债券收益率将走高。在“彭博收盘”节目中，Knapp 还讨论了股票和美元的前景。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-06/bond-yields-are-headed-higher-barry-knapp-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 20:40:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
